title: Ep. - 388 - LEAH MCSWEENEY REVIEWS BACHELOR IN PARADISE AJ GALANTE FROM UNTOLD ON NETFLIX
description:
Leah McSweeney from Real Housewives of New York reviews Bachelor in Paradise.

 

A.J. Galante from Netflix’s UNTOLD: Crime and Penalties, which dives into the short-lived success of the minor league hockey team that a mafia-tied trash magnate bought for his 17-year-old son to run, Connecticut’s Danbury Trashers. The riveting true crime storylines the FBI’s takedown of the roaring, brawling, bruising, bananas Danbury Trashers, along with their owner Jimmy Galante.
